            我能识别眼睛幽蓝的女子。她们是苔藓。黑暗给她们水分，生命甜美而脆弱。 (<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/34364101/">查看原文</a>)

            <div class="blockquote-extra">
              <div class='blockquote-meta'>
                <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/63597321/" class="author-avatar">
